column22: The overall appearance and colour of the water, surf, and sky.

column24: An ocean liner crosses the horizon. It leaves a trail of smoke in the blue sky.
column25: A beautiful air balloon appears with four people aboard. The balloon drifts past you, almost directly overhead. The passengers wave and smile. You wave and smile back at them.
column26: The overall appearance of the station viewed from in front of the main entrance.

column29: You walk to the platform and observe other passengers and the railway lines. A train arrives. You climb aboard.
column30: The overall appearance and design of the garden.
